OL,6,FFamilies throughout the country are
OL,7,Fwaiting for answers ahead of the
OL,8,FInfected Blood Inquiry findings being
OL,9,Freleased next week.
OL,11,FMany families have been waiting
OL,12,Fanxiously for decades looking for
OL,13,Fanswers.
OL,15,FJohn Strachan died in 1987 just two
OL,16,Fweeks before his son Bob turned nine,
OL,17,Fwho had to grow up with the stigma of
OL,18,Fhis dad having died from HIV at a time
OL,19,Fwhere little was known about the
OL,20,Finfection.
