OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Bob Strachan,
OL,7,Fson of John, said: "My dad didn't hug
OL,8,Fmyself or even kiss my mum because he
OL,9,Fdidn't know how this was passed on.
OL,11,F"My father contracted HIV in the early
OL,12,Feighties and sadly died in 1987. But
OL,13,Fmy mum had told me that he died of
OL,14,Fkidney failure. And that was what I
OL,15,Fbelieve until my teens.
OL,17,F"Then mum sat me down and told me the
OL,18,Ffull story.
