OL,6,F"There was a lot of ignorance around
OL,7,Fit, so it's just really hard to think
OL,8,Fabout, something that was life
OL,9,Fchanging and life ending not just for
OL,10,Fthat person, but for everyone around
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"It's the condition of life leading up
OL,14,Fto that. It's dealing with our mental
OL,15,Fhealth after this and throughout all
OL,16,Fof our lives."
