OL,6,FJohn caught HIV from an infected blood
OL,7,Ftransfusion, and his family were so
OL,8,Faffected by the stigma, they moved
OL,9,Ffrom Peterhead to New Zealand, then
OL,10,FCanada, before coming back to . And
OL,11,FBob has now settled in .
OL,13,FBob's daughter never had the chance to
OL,14,Fmeet her grandfather, but has still
OL,15,Fbeen affected by this part of their
OL,16,Ffamily history.
