OL,6,FBobbi Strachan said: "I would get
OL,7,Freally emotional and I would talk
OL,8,Fabout certain things because grandad
OL,9,Fsounded like such an amazing person,
OL,10,Fand I would have loved to have got to
OL,11,Fknow him.
OL,13,F"I'm 22-years-old and this has been
OL,14,Fgoing on double my life, forty years,
OL,15,Fand it caused a lot of issues.
OL,17,F"And so I'm really hoping that, you
OL,18,Fknow, this brings closure to my
OL,19,Fgrandma and my dad and so many other
OL,20,Ffamilies. It's really important."
